divs: sighting detailsi took a picture of my pool yesterday afternoon with my cell phone looking toward the east. this morning i zoomed in to get a closer look, to my surprise i seen 2 objects what seemed like 2 birds, then i looked to the right of the picture and seen one more object, they look equally shaped and almost equally spaced apart.. i'm usually a sky\star gazer and never noticed these objects while i was sitting there. they showed up in my photo. i'm curious what they could be.
